name: Tram With Man by Pam Voth

metadata.name: Tram With Man #1
metadata.description: In "Tram with Man," tranquility dances on the edge of chaos. Amidst the bustling city of Lisbon, Portugal, yellow trams traverse the steep hills carrying hordes of tourists to historic sites. Perhaps contemplating the crowded masses he will face today, a conductor takes a quiet moment for himself.
